contentrichtext.text: '''BND''' may stand for: * ''[[Bundesnachrichtendienst]]'', German intelligence agency * [[Bank of North Dakota]] * [[Buy Nothing Day]] * [[Brunei dollar]] ([[ISO currency code]]) * [[Ordinary National Diploma|BTEC National Diploma]] * [[Brandon railway station]], Brandon, Suffolk, England; [[National Rail]] station code BND * [[Bulgarian New Democracy]], a Bulgarian centre-right party. * "BND", a song on [[No Doubt (No Doubt album)]] * The Russian way of saying [[VID (company)]], A Russian TV Company. * [http://www.aqute.biz/Bnd/Bnd bnd], a software toolkit for [[OSGi]] development. {{disambiguation}}
